Role Method Endpoint Description Admin PATCH <code>/api/v1/songs/{id}/review/</code> Approve or reject a song request. <p>Request Body:</p> <pre><code>{
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "rejection_reason": "Optional reason"
}
</code></pre> <p>Validation Rules:</p> <ul> <li><code>status</code>: Must be one of <code>APPROVED</code>, <code>REJECTED</code>.</li> <li><code>rejection_reason</code>: Required if status is <code>REJECTED</code>.</li> <li>Only songs with <code>PENDING</code> status can be reviewed.</li> </ul>
